====Egg Exclusive Pokemon==== {| class="wikitable" |- ! Pokemon !! Exception |- |[[File:Charmander.png|30px]] Charmander || - |- |[[File:Bulbasaur.png|30px]]Bulbasaur || - |- |[[File:Squirtle.png|30px]]Squirtle || - |- |[[File:Lapras.png|30px]]Lapras || - |- |[[File:Hitmonchan.png|30px]]Hitmonchan || - |- |[[File:Hitmonlee.png|30px]]Hitmonlee || - |- |[[File:Dratini.png|30px]]Dratini || - |- |[[File:Dragonair.png|30px]]Dragonair || Evolve Dratini |- |[[File:Dragonite.png|30px]]Dragonite || Evolve Dragonair |- |} [[Category:Regions]]

'''Kanto''' is the first [[region]] in the Pokéclicker world, where the player starts the game. The Pokedex for this region contains 151 Pokemon from Bulbasaur to Mew. Uniquely to this region, certain Pokemon can only be found in the [[Safari Zone]].
[[File:Pokeclickerkanto.png|thumb|A Town Map of the Kanto region]]
